parameters.name: subscription_id
parameters.label: Subscription ID
parameters.helpText: Pub/Sub subscription for reading input data. Must be a resource identifier in the format: projects/<project_id>/subscriptions/<subscription_name>

parameters.name: dataset_id
parameters.label: Dataset ID
parameters.helpText: BigQuery dataset for writing output data. Must be a resource identifier in the format: <project_id>:<dataset_name>
